<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TravelUp</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Color Palette */
            --primary-color: #26c6da;
            --primary-color-dark: #1e9cb0;
            --accent-color: #a0bac5;
            --text-dark: #2c3e50;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --background-light: #f4f7f9;
            --shadow-color: rgba(38, 198, 218, 0.15);
        }

        /* Global Resets and Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            background-color: var(--background-light);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 1rem 2rem; /* Added horizontal padding for better alignment */
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox for layout */
            justify-content: flex-end; /* Space between content */
            align-items: center; /* Center items vertically */
            color: var(--text-light);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px var(--shadow-color);
}

        .header a {
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        .header a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .section-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: var(--text-light);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px var(--shadow-color);
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
         h2 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(
                135deg, 
                var(--primary-color), 
                var(--primary-color-dark)
            );
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: var(--text-light);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: var(--text-light);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .section-container {
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a href="/loggedinhome">Home</a>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="section-container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h1>About TravelUp</h1>
            <p>Welcome to TravelUp! We are a passionate team dedicated to redefining travel experiences through innovation and personalization. Our mission is to make your journeys seamless, memorable, and truly extraordinary.</p>

            <p>At TravelUp, we harness the power of Smart AI to simplify trip planning and create tailored itineraries that align perfectly with your preferences. From choosing destinations to crafting the perfect schedule, our AI-driven tools ensure every detail is thoughtfully managed.</p>

            <p>To enhance your experience, our intelligent chatbot is available 24/7 to assist with your queries, offer real-time recommendations, and provide personalized support during your travels. Whether you need quick answers or travel advice, we're always here to help.</p>

            <p>Founded on the belief that travel transforms lives, TravelUp combines expert knowledge, cutting-edge technology, and a commitment to sustainable tourism. We craft journeys that connect you with the heart of every destination while supporting local communities and preserving the environment.</p>

            <p>Join us at TravelUp to explore the world smarter, better, and more sustainably!</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Begin Your Journey?</h2>
        <p>" Discover the world with us and create unforgettable memories."</p>
        <a href="/search" class="cta-button">Explore Destinations</a>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
